title: Question 6:
description: What is the current fee structure

fields.title: Answer:
fields.value:
At the time of writing, 2% is taken from your deposit per year, and 20% is taken from profits when harvested. 
Fees are subject to change. More details can be found here 
https://docs.yearn.finance/yearn-finance/yvaults/overview#yvault-fee-structure
